1) Bootstrap

    gem 'bootstrap-sass', '~> 3.3.5'
    gem 'sass-rails', '>= 3.2'
    References:
    http://getbootstrap.com
    https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap-sass
    https://github.com/rails/sass-rails


2) Devise

